---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service — Signario"
  description="Terms of Service for Signario."
>
  <Nav />

  <main class="pt-32 pb-24 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mb-12">Last updated: April 2026</p>

      <div class="space-y-8 text-slate-400 leading-relaxed text-sm">

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">1. Acceptance of terms</h2>
          <p>By accessing signario.io or signing up for the Signario waitlist, you agree to these Terms of Service. If you do not agree, please do not use our website.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">2. Description of service</h2>
          <p>Signario is an AI-powered customer feedback management tool for B2B product teams, currently in early access. Features and pricing are subject to change before general availability.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">3. Waitlist</h2>
          <p>Joining the waitlist grants no right to access the product. We will contact waitlist members personally. Founder pricing, where offered, is subject to separate agreement at the time of access invitation.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">4. Acceptable use</h2>
          <p>You agree not to misuse the website, submit false information, or attempt to disrupt the service. Automated scraping of the website is not permitted without written consent.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">5. Intellectual property</h2>
          <p>All content on signario.io, including copy, design, and code, is the property of Signario. You may not reproduce or distribute it without permission.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">6. Disclaimer of warranties</h2>
          <p>The website and any pre-launch materials are provided "as is" without warranty of any kind. We make no guarantees about uptime, accuracy, or fitness for a particular purpose.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">7. Limitation of liability</h2>
          <p>To the maximum extent permitted by law, Signario shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from use of the website or waitlist.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">8. Governing law</h2>
          <p>These terms are governed by applicable law. Disputes shall be resolved through good-faith negotiation before any legal proceedings.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">9. Changes</h2>
          <p>We may update these terms. Continued use of the website after changes constitutes acceptance. Material changes will be announced via email to waitlist members.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">10. Contact</h2>
          <p>Questions? Email <a href="mailto:hello@signario.io" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300">hello@signario.io</a>.</p>
        </section>

      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
